ZH: 他的胡子只长了寸多。
EN: His beard is only an inch long.

ZH: 这根铁棍长寸多。
EN: This iron rod is over a foot long.

ZH: 他正在测量这个房间有多少寸。
EN: He is measuring how many square inches this room is.

ZH: 这个箱子的尺寸是长寸，宽寸，高寸。
EN: The dimensions of this box are 12 inches long, 6 inches wide, and 8 inches tall.

ZH: 这匹布是寸。
EN: This piece of fabric is one inch.

ZH: 她只愿意留寸的头发。
EN: She only wants to leave an inch of hair.

ZH: 请把桌子往前寸一下。
EN: Please move the table forward by an inch.

ZH: 我的尺子废了，现在只有一把寸木棍。
EN: My ruler is broken, now I only have a stick that measures inches.

ZH: 我们餐馆的炉子是唯一可用的一寸。
EN: The stove in our restaurant is the only usable one.

ZH: 这部手机的厚度只有寸。
EN: The thickness of this phone is only an inch.

ZH: 这次地震使得整个城市都往北寸了。
EN: This earthquake shifted the entire city north by an inch.

ZH: 这支笔的硬度只有寸。
EN: The hardness of this pen is only one inch.

ZH: 这篮球场是标准比赛场地尺寸，即是长寸，宽寸。
EN: This basketball court is a standard playing area, which is 94 feet long and 50 feet wide.

ZH: 这枝铅笔的长度是寸。
EN: The length of this pencil is one inch.

ZH: 请把这本书合上，长寸，宽寸。
EN: Please close this book, it's 12 inches long and 9 inches wide.

ZH: 窗户的高宽尺寸是长寸，宽寸。
EN: The window's height and width dimensions are 24 inches by 36 inches.

ZH: 这个画框外框的厚度只有寸。
EN: The thickness of the outer frame of this picture frame is only an inch.

ZH: 当地的工厂推出了一种寸级外壳的手机。
EN: The local factory launched a phone with an inch-sized casing.

ZH: 这个封口袋只有寸大小，仅能放置一些小物品。
EN: This sealed bag is only an inch long and can only hold small items.
